    <label>M-1A4 Powered Helmet</label>
    <description>"The M-1A4 Powered Helmet transforms the trooper's perception of combat. Three-hundred-sixty degree awareness means nothing sneaks up on you—sensors feed visual, thermal, and tactical data directly into your field of view. Targeting reticules lock onto threats automatically. Squad status updates in real-time. This isn't just protection—it's total battlefield domination through information superiority. The helmet's indirect visual system and armored construction can stop rounds that would penetrate standard MI helmets. When sealed with the powered suit body, you're protected from vacuum, hostile atmospheres, and NBC threats."</description>
